

Strategy			Command

1. Enable Debug Logging		export TF_LOG=DEBUG

export TF_LOG=DEBUG
terraform apply

export TF_LOG=DEBUG
export TF_LOG_PATH="terraform-debug.log"
terraform apply

2. Validate Configuration		terraform validate


3. Plan Debugging			terraform plan -out=tfplan.binary

terraform plan -out=tfplan.binary
terraform show -json tfplan.binary > tfplan.json




4. State Inspection		terraform state list & terraform state show <resource>


5. Graph Visualization		terraform graph

terraform graph | dot -Tpng > graph.png



6. Console Testing	terraform console

terraform console
> var.instance_type
> aws_instance.example.public_ip

7. Provider Debugging		TF_LOG=DEBUG terraform apply
TF_LOG=DEBUG TF_LOG_PATH=terraform.log terraform apply


8. Enable Detailed Terraform Debugging
TF_LOG=TRACE terraform apply 2>&1 | tee terraform-debug.log




9. Dry-Run Debugging		terraform plan -target=<resource>
	terraform plan -target=azurerm_virtual_machine.example


10. Manual State Inspection	`cat terraform.tfstate
	cat terraform.tfstate | jq '.resources[] | {type, name}'
	
